Class RMIServiceInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • mapred.RMIServiceInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RMIServiceInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is used to reserve the RMI related info including dataNode's Registry port, service name, partition numbers, partition file path, taskNode's registry port and service name.
